# Walkthrough: AI Chat History Integration System

## Summary

Built a complete persistent AI chat history system with a unified sidebar, modern ChatGPT/Perplexity-inspired UI, and production-ready responsive design. All changes pass lint and build with zero errors.

---

## Architecture Changes

### Before â†’ After

```mermaid
graph LR
    subgraph Before
        A["/home â†’ Home.jsx<br/>(embedded sidebar)"]
        B["/chat/:id â†’ Chat.jsx<br/>(separate mini sidebar)"]
    end
    subgraph After
        C["Layout.jsx<br/>(Sidebar + Outlet)"]
        D["/home â†’ Home.jsx<br/>(clean welcome page)"]
        E["/chat/:id â†’ Chat.jsx<br/>(modern chat UI)"]
        C --> D
        C --> E
    end
```

**Key architectural shift**: Extracted a shared `Layout.jsx` wrapper with persistent `Sidebar.jsx` that appears on all authenticated pages via React Router nested routes. Eliminated duplicate sidebar implementations.

