## How to Test

1. Start the backend: `cd backend && npm run dev`
2. Start the frontend: `cd frontend/perplexity && npm run dev`
3. Login â†’ redirected to `/home`
4. Test sidebar chat list, new chat creation, chat navigation, message persistence, responsive layout
